(216, 'Vinfast rallies on after becoming world\'s third-most valuable automaker', 'The company made a blowout debut on Wall Street this month and has quickly grown in valuation to become the third-most valuable automaker - only behind Tesla and Toyota.  But Vinfast\'s small amount of publicly available shares has made the stock prone to volatility, with shares jumping or slumping more than 14% in 11 of the past 12 sessions.  Vinfast\'s shares were among the most actively watched on Stocktwits, a popular website with retail investors.', '2023-08-28 18:26:10', '2023-08-28 18:26:10'),
