(616, 'Dow Jones Rallies 300 Points With Jobs, Inflation Data On Deck; Tesla Rival Xpeng Surges On Didi Deal', 'The Dow Jones rallied 300 points Monday, as investors awaited this week\'s key jobs and inflation data. Tesla stock rival Xpeng surged.', '2023-08-29 06:05:17', '2023-08-29 06:05:17'),
