(621, 'Elon Musk Tests the First Non-Beta Tesla FSD—And It\'s Far From Perfect', 'Musk tested the upcoming FSD v12, which relies entirely on neural networks instead of hardcoding, in a 45-minute drive near Tesla\'s engineering headquarters.', '2023-08-29 06:18:42', '2023-08-29 06:18:42'),
