(945, 'NIO Earnings Are Coming. Investors Are Nervous.', 'Chinese EV start-up  NIO  is set to report second-quarter numbers Tuesday morning amid questions about competition, demand, pricing, and the Chinese economy.  A lot more than just bottom-line earnings will be investors’ focus.  Wall Street expects a per-share loss of about 33 cents a share from $1.3 billion in sales, according to Bloomberg.', '2023-08-29 08:20:16', '2023-08-29 08:20:16'),
