(1645, 'Tech Analyst Dan Ives Says Tesla Just Turned This Huge Financial Burden Into a $20 Billion Revenue Opportunity', 'The past couple of years have been a rollercoaster thrill ride for Tesla (NASDAQ: TSLA) investors.  The biggest of these is the mad dash by a growing number of automakers to join the Tesla Supercharger Network and adopt its North American Charging Standard (NACS) connector, which is quickly becoming the de facto industry standard.  One Wall Street analyst believes this will add billions in annual revenue to Tesla\'s coffers.', '2023-08-29 12:18:49', '2023-08-29 12:18:49'),
